<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Careers & Opportunities | The Admission Architect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style> body { padding-top: 0 !important; } </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="landing-hero" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 150, 136, 0.9), rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">Career Opportunities</h1>
        <p>Launch your global career with post-study work options in the UK.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Building Your Resume Abroad</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            The UK is an incredible place to launch a career. International students have the right to work part-time up to 20 hours per week during term time, which helps cover living costs and builds valuable local experience.
        </p>

        <div style="background: #E0F2F1; border-left: 5px solid #009688; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #00796B;">The Graduate Route Visa</h3>
            <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">Upon successfully completing your Bachelor's or Master's degree, you are eligible to apply for the Graduate Route Visa. This allows you to stay in the UK for <strong>2 full years</strong> (3 years for PhD graduates) to work, or look for work, at any skill level without needing a company sponsor.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Top industries currently hiring international graduates include Healthcare, IT & Software Engineering, Business Analytics, and Finance. Our career counselors assist you with CV building and mock interviews to prepare you for the competitive job market.
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="/login" class="calc-btn-primary" style="background: #009688; display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 15px 40px;">Sign In to Access Career Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>